UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc6`='Caught him, huh? Good for you. I\'m surprised that was Slim.$B$BI\'ll be honest, I never thought I\'d miss the excitement of some of the more devious underground activities. I guess old habits die hard. Don\'t mention that to Elling--he\'d probably try and get me to come back to Stormwind if he heard I missed the action.$B$BI\'m glad I could at least be of a little service to you while you were in Menethil. If you need anything else, just ask.' WHERE `word_id` = 135233; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=1249
